attributes.name: onPlaceUpdate
attributes.default_value: async function onPlaceUpdate(expression, place){     let outgoingArcs = await expression.getOutgoingRelationsByInstanceUUID(place.uuid, "1bab6460-3aea-46b2-89e5-c436e3e194c5");     for (let arc of outgoingArcs){         let transition = await expression.getDestinationByRelInstanceUUID(arc.uuid);         if (transition.uuid_class=="123bd2cf-c79d-4e31-88e5-c71ee559535b"){             await isFireable(transition);         }     }     async function isConnected(transition){         const incomingArcs = await expression.getIncomingRelationsByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid,"1bab6460-3aea-46b2-89e5-c436e3e194c5");         const outgoingArcs = await expression.getOutgoingRelationsByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid, "1bab6460-3aea-46b2-89e5-c436e3e194c5");         const hasIncoming = incomingArcs.length != 0 ? "true" : "false";         const hasOutgoing = outgoingArcs.length != 0 ? "true" : "false";         if (hasIncoming && incomingArcs) {             await expression.setAttrvalByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid, "8de345ad-c636-48ad-a53d-df5836b135cd", hasIncoming);             await expression.checkForVisualizationUpdateByAttributeUUID(transition.uuid, "8de345ad-c636-48ad-a53d-df5836b135cd");         }         if (hasOutgoing && outgoingArcs) {             await expression.setAttrvalByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid, "e72a4720-4cf9-412f-ab6b-dddf27b6d435", hasOutgoing);             await expression.checkForVisualizationUpdateByAttributeUUID(transition.uuid, "e72a4720-4cf9-412f-ab6b-dddf27b6d435");         }             return hasIncoming == "true" && hasOutgoing == "true";     }     async function isFireable(transition){         let fireable = await isConnected(transition);         if (fireable){             const incomingArcs = await expression.getIncomingRelationsByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid, "1bab6460-3aea-46b2-89e5-c436e3e194c5");             for (let arc of incomingArcs){                 let incomingPlace = await expression.getSourceByRelInstanceUUID(arc.uuid);                 let weight = parseInt(await expression.attrvalByInst("9e68a132-3d72-4af2-8d0e-b238af904a29", arc.uuid)) || 1;                 let tokens = parseInt(await expression.attrvalByInst("e4943c7e-e6f0-4f0f-b26b-7860416a7c63", incomingPlace.uuid)) || 0;                 if (tokens < weight){                 fireable = false;                  break;                   }             }         }         await expression.setAttrvalByInstanceUUID(transition.uuid, "7524cc99-82e0-4ca4-b752-10c21f7b0f57", fireable? "true":"false");              await expression.checkForVisualizationUpdateByAttributeUUID(transition.uuid, "7524cc99-82e0-4ca4-b752-10c21f7b0f57");         return fireable;      } }
